al-chinas-challenge-build-its-own-jet-engine-c919-it-seeks-aviation-self-reliance?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>前美国海军情报官员：解放军可能尚未做好2030年前对台湾发动大规模两栖攻击的准备</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3251674/pla-may-not-be-ready-major-amphibious-attack-taiwan-2030-ex-us-navy-intelligence-officer?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>退役美国海军情报官员 J. 迈克尔·达姆 (J. Michael Dahm) 写道，对台湾进行任何重大攻击的关键的两栖登陆和后勤技能范围可能要到 2030 年代中期才会出现。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 10:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3251674/pla-may-not-be-ready-major-amphibious-attack-taiwan-2030-ex-us-navy-intelligence-officer?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>联合国维和行动结束后，中国将与马里保持严格的经济关系</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251351/china-tipped-keep-mali-ties-strictly-economic-un-peacekeeping-mission-wraps?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>观察人士预计，中国将只关注马里的贸易和商业往来，这符合避免直接干预复杂冲突的一贯政策。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 08:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251351/china-tipped-keep-mali-ties-strictly-economic-un-peacekeeping-mission-wraps?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>龙年中国游客卷土重来，除夕夜出游人数达1.95亿人次</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3251661/chinese-travellers-back-roar-year-dragon-195-million-trips-marking-lunar-new-years-eve?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>领先的旅游服务公司报告称，随着数亿人在全国各地过春节假期，人数远高于大流行前的水平。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 06:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3251661/chinese-travellers-back-roar-year-dragon-195-million-trips-marking-lunar-new-years-eve?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国冰雕之城哈尔滨在后疫情时代的复兴中旅游业蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251556/tourism-booms-chinas-ice-sculpture-city-harbin-post-covid-revival?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>今年节日的游客数量创下了历史新高，社